  "title": "Air Cargo Operations Officer (East / Shift Work / 5.5-Day Week)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle import/export shipments efficiently, including documents like HAWB, MAWB, billing, and pre-alerts.</li>\n  <li>Prepare accurate shipping documents: invoice, packing list, B/L, AWB, L/C, etc.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, shipping agents, contractors, ports, and truckers.</li>\n  <li>Track and manage daily export schedules.</li>\n  <li>Keep customer contact records up to date.</li>\n  <li>Improve freight processes through continuous improvement initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Answer customer queries locally and abroad.</li>\n  <li>Finalize P/L reports on time.</li>\n  <li>Manage basic warehouse operations.</li>\n  <li>Follow internal customer guidelines and SOPs.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with sales, especially on air freight cases.</li>\n  <li>Submit accurate carrier/co-loader declarations.</li>\n  <li>Support with any ad hoc duties assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
